      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior shows significant signs of age, including several rusted body panels, deep scratches, and multiple dents. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several large tears and persistent stains, and some electronic components are non-functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs but will require immediate repairs to the suspension and exhaust system to be truly roadworthy. This would be an ideal project for someone looking to restore a vehicle or for parts.",
