    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a parts car. The engine currently runs roughly and will likely require a major overhaul or replacement soon, and the transmission shifts harshly between gears. On the exterior, there is significant paint oxidation, several deep dents, and noticeable rust bubbling along the wheel arches and rocker panels. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and a non-functional air conditioning system. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
